# Plan 9: Admin Panel - Blog Management

## Goal
Build the blog management interface with a WYSIWYG editor.

## Tasks
- [ ] Install `tiptap` or `lexical` for the rich text editor.
- [ ] Create `app/admin/blog/page.tsx` (list view) and `app/admin/blog/new/page.tsx` (editor).
- [ ] Implement the editor with toolbar (bold, italic, headings, links).
- [ ] Add image upload functionality within the editor.
- [ ] Create Server Actions to save/update posts.
- [ ] Add fields for SEO metadata (title, description) and tags.
